<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p local-id=3D"a75af42cb855">We recommend you export this letter as a pdf o=
r word document once you are finished.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"5cd3a80d4963"></p>
<p local-id=3D"9e84b12b5304"><span data-colorid=3D"qsrk7qzppp">&lt;Type // =
to add a date&gt;</span></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"9819292a1f17" id=3D"Employeepromotionletter-Dear<Employeena=
me>,"><img class=3D"emoticon emoticon-laugh" data-emoji-id=3D"1f600" data-e=
moji-shortname=3D":grinning:" data-emoji-fallback=3D"\uD83D\uDE00" src=3D"1=
7ebb4ac8aef77cec9a0156ecda5283ba9a94904f7721b6bbe79d63a064e890a" width=3D"1=
6" height=3D"16" data-emoticon-name=3D"laugh" alt=3D"(big grin)">&nbsp;Dear=
 <span data-colorid=3D"ofrppeujgf">&lt;Employee name&gt;</span>,</h2>
<p local-id=3D"07d4b849bd29">Congratulations on your promotion to the posit=
ion of <span data-colorid=3D"qgne926pxp">&lt;Job title&gt;</span>, effectiv=
e <span data-colorid=3D"vw2pdc82xg">&lt;Type // to add a date&gt;</span>. W=
e appreciate your hard work and commitment to the <span data-colorid=3D"fto=
64ylr40">&lt;Company name&gt;</span> team for the last <span data-colorid=
=3D"xgy6o04lit">&lt;Add number&gt;</span> years.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e581f198d348">The annual salary for this position will be <s=
pan data-colorid=3D"ciq6da3p7b">&lt;Salary number&gt;</span> paid on a <spa=
n data-colorid=3D"yyfhnc9hos">&lt;weekly/biweekly/monthly/annual&gt;</span>=
 basis. You will report directly to <span data-colorid=3D"gmohqil55c">&lt;N=
ame of manager, Job title&gt;. &lt;Name of manager&gt;</span> is excited ab=
out your new role and will be reaching out to discuss any new job responsib=
ilities and transition plans.</p>
<p local-id=3D"0465280cabc7">Again, congratulations on the new position. Pl=
ease let me know if you have any questions regarding your compensation and =
benefits package.</p>
<p local-id=3D"13d4502babe7">Sincerely,</p>
<p local-id=3D"27d95456e571"></p>
